# Project Structure

This is a monorepo managed with bun workspaces.

- The main web application is an Astro blog located in `[apps/website](mdc:apps/website)`.
  - The main entry page is `[apps/website/src/pages/index.astro](mdc:apps/website/src/pages/index.astro)`.
  - React components can be found in `[apps/website/src/components/react](mdc:apps/website/src/components/react)`.
- Infrastructure is defined using SST (Serverless Stack Toolkit).
  - The main configuration file is `[sst.config.ts](mdc:sst.config.ts)`.
  - Infrastructure modules are located in the `[infra](mdc:infra)` directory.
- Shared packages (if any) would reside in the `[packages](mdc:packages)` directory.
